{"tid":2198196,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"出法律書遭建制狙擊 檢控官離職","createTime":"2020-09-11T07:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T09:25:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6229373829488d1f99501d9424d6753fcabde868","tid":2198196,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:33:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200911/LBO7KQITFNDVZJLCIL3JFBXSBI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200911%2FLBO7KQITFNDVZJLCIL3JFBXSBI%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fuTimN4xbKJd0qqIWjmG9ok%3D&h=83aa13fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200911%2FLBO7KQITFNDVZJLCIL3JFBXSBI%2F&h=652d9d3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200911/LBO7KQITFNDVZJLCIL3JFBXSBI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n出法律書遭建制狙擊 檢控官離職<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bIyUg22bMrcM0mmSIvc2UJX9pu8=/720x500/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NHP747WSDFAQ5O3QT2KNI25UKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbIyUg22bMrcM0mmSIvc2UJX9pu8%3D%2F720x500%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNHP747WSDFAQ5O3QT2KNI25UKE.jpg&h=1997515f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《一讀就懂 ! 孩子必須知的法律常識》<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民建聯葛珮帆、蔣麗芸分別於3月及4月向立法會司法及法律事務委員會發信，質疑律政司刑事檢控科檢控官翁達揚出版一本兒童法律常識書籍中，教導青少年避開法律陷阱，又不滿法官在審理反修例案件量刑起點過低。律政司回覆指，該名檢控人員早前已被調離崗位及離職，又稱法庭是因應案件判刑因素達致適當刑罰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n談法律權益 葛珮帆投訴<br />\n<br />\n時任律政司刑事檢控科檢控官翁達揚去年9月出版《一讀就懂 ! 孩子必須知的法律常識》一書（圖），談法律權益和知識，惟被葛珮帆質疑教導青少年疑犯避開法律陷阱，涉利益衝突及公職人員行為失當，要求律政司交代。<br />\n<br />\n律政司回覆指，知悉事件後，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於蔣麗芸指部份法官在審理反修例案件量刑起點過低，。。。。。。"},{"pid":"d8844187f013c50dcd11b884ae55bd086afbe123","tid":2198196,"uid":49329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08: